                <note rend="inline" type="source">862.4016/412: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Germany (<persName type="from">Gordon</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-04-05T14:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 5, 1933—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>38. Your 56, April 4, 6 p.m. and 57, April 5, Noon. We have decided not to issue
                    a statement at the present juncture, as the situation here no longer offers a
                    suitable occasion for so doing.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
